        <Summary xml:lang="en">Qt bindings for gpgme</Summary>
        <Description xml:lang="en">GPGME (GnuPG Made Easy) is a C language library that allows to add support for cryptography to a program. It is designed to make access to public key crypto engines like GnuPG or GpgSM easier for applications. GPGME provides a high-level crypto API for encryption, decryption, signing, signature verification and key management.
</Description>
